      "layout": "The page maintains a centered, maximal-width content area rather than full-bleed. The hero section presents very large, impactful typography as the primary visual element. Content is arranged in stacked blocks with significant vertical separation, indicated by clear section gaps. Distinct horizontal dividers in black reinforce structural breaks. Navigation is a minimalist top bar with ghost utility links and discrete bordered buttons, emphasizing clear boundaries over seamless flow.",
      "imagery": "The site's visual language for imagery is minimal and functional, featuring dark, distinct icons or symbolic graphics rather than photography or detailed illustrations. Icons are solid-filled or outlined in black, with sharp, geometric forms. The large '404' graphic appears to be a distorted, monumental typographic element rather than a traditional image, reinforcing a strong, graphic-design-led aesthetic. Imagery serves a purely indicative or decorative function, always adhering to the monochrome palette and angular style, never for atmosphere or detailed content explanation. Density is image-sparse, prioritizing text and structural elements.",
